how can you stop a rabbit from biting you when approaching the rabbit do so slowly and make no sudden moves or loud noises without getting too close let it sniff your hand then slowly reach over the top of its head and gently rub it directly behind the ears once you have shown the rabbit that you do not intend to hurt it and have gained its trust this may take several attempts and require lots of patience you can then gently pick it up stroke it as long as you are calm and quiet at all times the rabbit should realise that you mean no harm and that you are not a threat Domestic rabbit Diving Aerial (dance move) Breastfeeding Microphone Combine (Half-Life 2) Quake III Arena Cat Guinea pig Milton H. Erickson Shaggy dog story Rabbit Internal ballistics Swimming The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe Domestic violence Housebreaking Ferret Textile manufacturing Unreal Military history of the United Kingdom during World War II Treehouse of Horror V Loudspeaker Chinchilla Campfire Weighting filter Dog Supporting Characters (Xenogears) Equine conformation Lightning Prisoner's dilemma Table tennis Ear Kakapo First aid Fast bowling The Death Gate Cycle Horse The Beatles Magic (illusion) Pakistani cricket team in West Indies in 2005 Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Decibel Eye Second Battle of the Atlantic Four-stroke cycle Batting (cricket) Hun-Apu Tobacco smoking Breaststroke Social rule Sonic X USS Sea Dog (SS-401) Doom enemies Donald Neilson Harp Gramophone record Sudoku StarCraft: Uprising Sin City Violin Level crossing Bugs Bunny Who Framed Roger Rabbit Vegeta Isle of Portland Gag (BDSM) Animal communication Tasmanian Devil Horse breaking Pitaten EastEnders Shark One Piece minor characters Bangladeshi cricket team in Sri Lanka in 2005-06 Falconry Strap-on dildo Animal testing 24 Hours of Le Mans Hearing aid Martial art Gun safety Timpani Tinnitus Antenna (radio) Time travel Sonic Heroes Mickey Mouse Transactional analysis Amami Rabbit The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy Primary